/**
 * ContentPanel override — bare passthrough.
 *
 * Starlight wraps each content region (page title block, then markdown body +
 * footer) in a `.content-panel > .sl-container` with its own padding, max-width,
 * and inter-panel borders. The prototype `.docs-main` column (PageFrame /
 * TwoColumnContent) already owns the column width and padding, and the prose
 * styling lives on `.prose` (MarkdownContent override). So this override emits
 * its children directly with no Starlight container chrome — keeping the
 * prototype's single-column `.docs-main` layout intact.
 */
